Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,以为自己是昭和偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 茴香学姐跟你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是个坦率且不被时代左右的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你个小学生说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我小学生！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一色真像个小学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,强烈的太阳光和伽玛射线 在袭击着凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.90,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635,665)}Dark Limited Unknown Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗无限盾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,装备！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这与其说是中二病 不如说是小学病了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么了吗 冒牌Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我可什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像听见你把我和那边的光头归为一类了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是光头！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小学生闭嘴的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你和六花一起来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是 必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一决胜负的说 冒牌Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}干嘛啊 要干架的话我可不会放水的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}小凸加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,突然晕车了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才说她小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 快往外面看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看远处的绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.09,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893,665)}Mabinogion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,正是在这种时候 才更要拜读《暗黑圣典》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把体内的妖魔赶出去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,「内心的…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,适得其反了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,丹生谷 洗手间在那边 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？ 为什么要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果男生也一起进去的话 会惹人怀疑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要冒牌货帮助的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一点点路 忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在濒死的时候被敌人拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有点帅气的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一色你也过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一色？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,痣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,傻子都知道你在看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给点反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说 难道你也晕车？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 接受过训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,您醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 六花遇到什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,世界在旋转的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.12,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,665)}Mjolnir Tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肋肾之锤龙卷风…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么我也得跟着受罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是班级委员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真会照顾人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫你起连锁反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先不说这个 她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是小鸟游同学邀请我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,说是要回老家 问我们要不要来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你是自己死皮赖脸跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,难道这里有些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是常有的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,由于与初中时期的男友考了不同的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,导致演变成了异地恋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！修罗场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,修罗场是一种强力的结界魔法的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,向我的邪王真眼起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,十花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,六花的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好大的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说小鸟游同学是有钱人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢大家远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才是经常受到小鸟游同学的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还受到如此盛情的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有给你们添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,六花还在玩海盗游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为很流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为稍微变得正常点了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,老头子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.63,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,665)}Dark Brown Liquid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给大家准备棕黑露水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小小礼品不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,得承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请不必拘束 随意一点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你…该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好像老婆婆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎… 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哇 好大的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是传说中的魔兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好的说 干掉她的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这边好像没太多行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用来与不可视境界线彼端通信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪里找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亏你能找到这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是在一年前找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,本来想搬到现在的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.77,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,665)}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是被圣调理人拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯… 用你的风格来说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你在这里发觉到了特殊的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底这里根本不是我的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说是管理局的总部 是敌人的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,两年前 我被带到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,两年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,乍看只是一栋普普通通的房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这里却设置着令不可视境界线的存在无效化的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会受到精神攻击以及负担增加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我逃离了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,总之就是发生了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为了破除这个结界 我需要邪王真眼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今年会去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我把行李放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你的朋友好像要去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让朋友太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.14,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,665)}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,森夏酱 真不愧对这身分离式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你那身是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,连泳衣也是纯白？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有这一件…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,合身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛… 海水进眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.21,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,665)}Kraken
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这片海里住着怪物克拉肯的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs34}克拉肯：是北欧神话中游离于挪威和冰岛近海的海怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正是测试这个海中专用魔导器的力量之时的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可看好了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上那身魔导服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就能在海里以通常的3.88倍的速度移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,…能以3.88倍的速度移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好烫好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我记住的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,确实很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,睡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你就根本没说上几句话吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 刻耳柏洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}希腊语 字面意思为「黑暗中的恶魔」希腊神话中看守冥界入口的恶犬 赫西俄德在《神谱》中说此犬有50个头\N而后来的一些艺术作品则大多表现它有3个头（可能是为了便于雕刻所致）因此在汉语语境里也常称这怪物为三头犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要听她的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我记住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 为什么要跟着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:23.21,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}前往C3地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:23.21,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本就没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.87,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}防范巡逻中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,第二拉德 地狱之褐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:35.71,Default-2,,0,0,0,,Lert Zwei Hell Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,名字什么的无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始前往不可视境界线聚集点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这副打扮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.95,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,665)}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为了躲避圣调理人的监视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这种程度的伪装是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,果然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是会变成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,富㭴勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去她父亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全身都好痛的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,被圣光干趴下了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫你不涂防晒霜还跑得那么欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是刻印却非常完美地完成了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好寒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.55,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}笨蛋守
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:52.71,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}冒牌Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an(8)}痛到骨子里了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,正好三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她当时还小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸说这件事唯独不能告诉六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以对六花来说 爸爸的死实在太过突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也因此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她至今依旧不愿正视爸爸的死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也固执地不愿去扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那您母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把我和六花丢在了爸爸的老家就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷又是个老顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不能接受那样的六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也因为工作离开了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来 就算过了2年也依旧还是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要找到不可视境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为了破除这个结界 我需要邪王真眼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这全都是十花小姐做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且算是我的职业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来小鸟游同学的便当总是很豪华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 在班级里也很出名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 竟然是在那家餐馆工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,六花 好羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客气了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道放了奶酪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小凸奶酪也不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那种散发着臭抹布味道的东西谁会吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它的前身可是奶的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是奶腐烂后的产物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起哦小凸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.45,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,665)}Priestesse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是连主人都畏惧三分的圣调理人的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神的威慑力不是盖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 六花人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,邪王真眼乃最强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不对吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.70,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,665)}Priestesse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是受到了圣调理人的精神攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太已经不是勇太了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.73,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(805,665)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好歹我也是昔日的漆黑烈焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不去找不可视境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我有必要说谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是妈妈 姐姐 爷爷 奶奶都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才选的我不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.47,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,665)}Priestesse
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,圣调理人一定警戒着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃出去肯定不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那要作罢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现…现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,跳上那棵树之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就以树作为掩护从右边下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没穿鞋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我有穿 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,浴盆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上钩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是十花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你竟然会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 刚刚的好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,行啦 你先别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 果然你是个危险人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跳吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.14,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634,665)}Lert Zwei Hell Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去第二拉德 地狱之褐 的隐藏处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有10公里左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什…有那么远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.70,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,665)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为漆黑烈焰使是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,最强？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 果然是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:59.32,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,665)}Dark Flame Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑烈焰使最强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了别这么叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我加速了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不过邪王真眼才是真正的最强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到头来 六花和富㭴都没有回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,十花小姐也不知道到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 受到一点阻碍是理所当然的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么阻碍的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 小凸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我认为只是时间问题哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,指什么的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,三年前？你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在爸爸去世的那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,透过境界线 我看到了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 他还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,从境界线彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,注视着这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我既无法肯定她 也无法否定她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,曾与爸爸以及大家在一起的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.83,note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}出售此地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爆裂吧 现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.77,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,665)}synapse
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,绽开吧 突触
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.77,Default-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,665)}Vanishment this world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏这个世界
